Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.35,0:00:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the sky, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.75,0:00:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.34,0:00:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the jet limit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart-warming la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.14,0:00:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a million-horsepower engine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.65,0:00:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.62,0:00:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off your guard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.65,0:00:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a seven-force power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.23,0:01:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.73,0:01:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolf! Wolf's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.11,0:01:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it. That liar boy fooled us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolf! Wolf's here! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm going to be fooled again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.08,0:01:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true this time! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The liar boy who used to lie all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,finally got eaten by the wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Good job, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.90,0:01:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is a moral in this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.05,0:01:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Does anyone know what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.14,0:01:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes. -Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes! -Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes... -Shibukaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.57,0:02:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What moral does it have?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.07,0:02:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,When you lie, you have to do it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Those who laughed, you wait and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.16,0:02:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shibukaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... What do you call it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,if you keep lying all the time, you will pay dearly one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Lying is the start of a theft. You shouldn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Atom is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Robots are designed to not lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.11,0:02:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! You are dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What would happen\Nif a robot could tell lies?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.78,0:02:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Robot Who Lied
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.17,0:03:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Here. -Thank you, Thor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's a pretty shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-Really? Is it really pretty? -Really. It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What color is it? White? Blue? Or pink?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.39,0:03:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's clear like the color of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes, will it not get cured forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor told me it will get cured. It will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.87,0:03:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-Of course! -Thor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor, bring Kozue in. There are visiting students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the crust lab. How lively they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... About that big earthquake that is about to happen near the East Sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the one in the newspaper? It's all right lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.75,0:04:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? I'm afraid of earthquakes and lightnings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor, I have to host the visiting students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-Could you go to the measuring room instead of me? -Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that a robot assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He's a smart assistant. He helps a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised. You look exactly like Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, it really does look like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:04:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So the cause of an earthquake is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the slanted or cut crusts
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is because the crusts all over the world
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.86,0:05:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-is moving all the time. -Gosh, it's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go see the computer in the measuring room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-What? If we get caught, the beard one will scold us. -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you afraid of the teacher? I can't hang out with cowards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I'm coming. Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Atom, are you going to keep pretending you are good? -I'm coming too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I imagining things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-How nice. -Let's ask them to let us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Minamizu Crust Lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, abnormal uplift is continuing for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the ocean floor of the Izu peninsula.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,According to computer prediction, a big earthquake could happen today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. If that information leaks, there will be great panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.39,0:06:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it a secret until we have a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I will never tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh! Gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-Big earthquake. Earthquake is coming! -Earthquake is coming! Earthquake! Trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh, wh, what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure? Mr. Doumoto. Bi... Big... Earthquake...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:07:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said such thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Assistant robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He heard us talking with the Weather Service on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor. Thor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He flew out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Earthquake is coming! Earthquake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Big earthquake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Earthquake is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear it? Earthquake is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an assistant at the crust lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-Run! Help! -Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Earthquake is coming! Earthquake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.07,0:08:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Mr. Doumoto, it's a mistake that a big earthquake is coming, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, go down to the town and quench a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand? Don't let it catch that gas tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If that explodes, Shimoda town will be exterminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fireman, did everyone evacuate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah, evacuation is complete. -Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You never let out such warning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistake? Assistant robot's? Gosh! Dang it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:10:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Make immediate arrangements! Arrest the robot called Thor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.94,0:10:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The earthquake warning was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone finds the assistant robot of the crust lab, please report.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where in the world that robot has gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch that robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thank goodness. You sure should be appreciated. -I'm glad I could be a help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's that one! The one that lied about earthquake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's that robot. -That robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the one who spread the rumor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.48,0:10:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's you for sure! -It's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not me. You are mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:10:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Thor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You! You are under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.64,0:11:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's resisting. You can shoot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's running. Shoot! Shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you make such terrible lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! It's dangerous. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tracks are crooked inside that tunnel, because of landslide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's true. -Thor! I found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor, why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I went inside and checked. It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So... Where is the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He went out to the other exit already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that boy! What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Thor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ah, the liar robot has returned. -It's the robot that spread the rumor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thor... -What in the world happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What a mystery for a robot to lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, I'm responsible for what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you why.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! Thor is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-What did you do with Thor? -Atom, I turned off the energy switch now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, come over here. Atom, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost my wife a year ago through an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter Kozue lost her eyesight in that accident as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Her eyes cannot be cured with current medical techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My assistant Thor is Kozue's best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A robot that cannot lie would tell about Kozue's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She already lost her mother; if she hears that she also lost her eyesight,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she would get shocked and abandon her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So I made a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to fix Thor's discrimination circuit
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and made him tell opposite things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This one worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor kept telling my daughter that she will get cured for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So my daughter could gain hope and stand back up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. There was such story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mr. Doumoto,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I do understand your feelings, but it's dangerous for robots to not make correct decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right. It has made the worst result.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.36,0:16:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell the truth to my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fix Thor. Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is nobody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor was here. Thor, wake up. There's a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Energy switch is off. A robot would never take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.16,0:17:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thor, there's a phone call. Take it. -Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is the crust lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be that assistant that lied?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Put me through the manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong? Speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Danger! There's a sign of a big earthquake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You again? I won't get fooled this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimoda police? A big earthquake is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please evacuate people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you still trying to spread such rumor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to smash you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! It's not a lie! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss, please evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's horrible! A big earthquake is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please evacuate. You should go up that hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to let townspeople know from now on. Please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.49,0:18:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Atom, please take care of my miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he stupid? Nobody's going to get fooled now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, Thor's discrimination circuit has been fixed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the earthquake is coming for real... Oh my gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, a big earthquake is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please evacuate to the emergency evacuation place!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Earthquake is coming! Hurry, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-You liar robot! -Are you going to fool us again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is true! Please trust me. Big earthquake is coming! Please evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Get rid of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Get rid of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.49,0:19:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-He's trying to make us fools. -Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Big earthquake.. is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Whatever! -You liar robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Earthquake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Save us, save us...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, get out! Help people evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Thor...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor! Thor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor Thor. It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.74,0:21:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor! Thor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor, are you all right? If you are there, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it Thor there? Thor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Answer me if you are okay, Thor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.87,0:21:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness, Thor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.16,0:21:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have some more rescue work to do. You should stay in a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.36,0:21:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.60,0:21:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, Atom lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom didn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.98,0:22:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom imitated Thor to calm Kozue down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.87,0:22:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom is a great robot to be able to imitate someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom's a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.88,0:22:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mountain cabin in snowstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here to ski with my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl came for help when everyone was asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.59,0:22:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Horett?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.49,0:22:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Aliens that suck up the Earth's water.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Several discuses invade the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.18,0:22:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Horett, what happened in Alsore?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy, "The Girl from Alsore." Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.99,0:22:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy "The Girl from Alsore"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.01,0:23:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms and legs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.03,0:23:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,fly over the sky with a jet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.54,0:23:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.66,0:23:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.41,0:23:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside my waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.36,0:23:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,a machine gun's light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.89,0:23:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.00,0:23:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Searchlight's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.84,0:23:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser Blast's hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.42,0:23:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven powers, Wa Wa Wa Wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.63,0:23:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight for the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.89,0:24:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go together
